title: Michi Marshall | Who Cheats More Women or Men?
description:
Michi Marshall, Kijafa Vick, Aja Crowder, Sharelle Rosado and Terricka Cromartie are back and kickoff Season 2 of I AM WOMAN. The women catch up and follow each other up on the details of their “Hot Girl” Summer.

The women then share their unique journeys of motherhood and discuss the differences between planned and unplanned parenthood. Sharelle goes on to discuss the importance of talking and educating their children on sex at an early age. Michi follows up with the question, Who cheats more? Women or men? The cast goes on to give their own unique perspective on this topic. Chef Tre joins the cast and gives his perspective on cheating while serving Cinnamon-Streusel Cake for desert.
